Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.46,0:00:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么　劫持巴士的恐怖分子的要求是?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是　他们要求立即撤出驻在阿尔泰的维和部队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:16.09,Note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}艾亚利兹行政府　赫其萨贡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及释放为接受审判而关押在我国Desperate监狱的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那基·泰·阿尔泰前大公
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波曼准将　报告情况
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Madam！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被占据的是往返于东部国境与首都之间的长途巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人质连同乘务员在内共十名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子们在车内设置了炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威胁说要求得不到满足的话就引爆炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.27,0:00:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下　总统选举迫在眼前的这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对应失误的话选情的前景将不容乐观
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是警察在处理么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12分钟之前　我们国家安全保障局已接过了指挥权
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:01:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DELTA-乙HiME部队已经在现场就位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据阁下的命令　任何时候都能突入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然对方手上有人质
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就不可轻易出手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对应要慎重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战名为「Silent Sea」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「寂静的大海」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过奖了　阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定静静地去完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的　已经像平常那样派人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她逃了~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是已经说过那种大小的石头已经没效了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:01:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-1　StandBy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-2　StandBy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-3　StandBy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Target in sight　任何时候都能射击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待机　多萝茜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须避免给对方造成不必要的刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平静地　冷静地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘~~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:28.69,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(475,10)}第二幕　暴·风·雨的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了　波曼准将
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将由我们这边安静地 秘密地…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我释放人质　堂堂正正地决一胜负！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿米特吉准将！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将！好好教训一下那些恐怖分子！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈拉德队长　表演个节目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:02:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好　冷静　冷静…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子已经迟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦　伊莉娜·伍兹?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　听得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西还真方便呐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?　爱莉卡·梦宫果然是在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车型呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了　胆小鬼　快回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个大嗓门的女人是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Meister遥·阿米特吉　克利桑德的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.61,0:03:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个破坏的阿米特吉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步走错后果可是不堪设想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白　那是我的馒头…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临时中断与石上候选人的谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴士劫持事件似乎有新的动态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄影机转向那边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出来的话我这边就要动手了　你们这群恶党
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来！过来的话我就把乘客全部炸死！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种试试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:04:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有艾亚利兹之魂的人才不会被炸弹什么的炸死呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是从加尔德罗贝赶来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责指挥的是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?　是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为DELTA的队长可是失职了呢　千绘·哈拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一些非正式的话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫神山消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连真白女王和Meister舞衣都…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧　我不是说过了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦　你认识Meister舞衣?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然认识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个开拉面店的女孩子吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说想开连锁店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就叫她本店设在艾亚利兹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经给了她忠告了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有　在那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下了要去搜寻真白陛下的字条
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister爱莉卡也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的追踪呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　已经找到了她所乘坐的长途巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴士?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个该不会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能解决吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点　我会帮你们一把的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的来历已经查明了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被认定是主谋者的人确实是原阿尔泰的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出身于陆军近卫师团的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现场状况怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被准将大闹一场以后　现在陷入了胶着状态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花市事件的情报还错综复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战略乙HiME限制交涉也近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允许失败呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人　要松饼吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛还这么镇静啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就是束手无策吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打破这种状况不就是我们的工作吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:05:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说强行突破什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请镇静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算放着不管　事态也总会有变化的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说不穿舞斗服就强行突破也太那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉·加拉格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要履行乙HiME的义务　跟舞斗服什么的没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好~好~　是气势吧　气势
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占据巴士的恐怖分子的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下届总统最合适的人选
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石上　石上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.93,0:06:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了大家的希望　期待的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亘·石上来倾听各位的要求了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁放那个家伙过去的?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位恐怖分子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊你这疯女人!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亘·石上　总算见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电视上狂批雪之和我的就是你吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不会明白那是为什么的　遥·阿米特吉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位国民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很担忧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此粗野又暴力的人居然进入国政的中枢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你更让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克利桑德和阿米特吉是艾亚利兹的智慧和灵魂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚下去　奇怪的帽子！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啰哩八嗦了　我们做个了断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大!　才不呢　那种事情是我做的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道为什么我能忍受如此的侮辱吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道为什么吗　遥·阿米特吉?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为交了女朋友啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错　正因为有爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才能突破重重困难
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后　我会为了爱肃清这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这份洋溢的感情　要向艾亚利兹全体国民…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前好象是个画人像的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好　大家注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么　在全世界前介绍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久将成为这个国家的第一夫人的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Sweet Honey 锵锵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　是这边吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真碍事　受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是烦这种蠢男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友绘·玛格丽特?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识这个家伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瓦尔基里部队的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为好玩而出卖自己人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大坏蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闭嘴　你们这群垃圾！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一夫人?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大错特错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲手解决了石上的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是新的总统候选人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友绘君　收手吧　看上去真让人痛心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧　请给我投下纯洁的一票　接受我的支配吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要自己在那大吵大闹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不给我认真谈判的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把这家伙的脑袋轰碎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾亚利兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇　准将　千绘前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不要察觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister爱莉卡·梦宫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是多么幸运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我放弃做家务而出来是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说　抢巴士的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看看这个奇特的面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是…瞧　就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「陨石破坏者」的爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那么了不起的事啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还没明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡　给我收拾掉这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的哟~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白不在　我现在没办法使用乙HiME的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要做什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次请你做我们的人质
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人…人质是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的孩子怎么这么傻啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚睡醒时谁都是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情真好　爱莉卡·梦宫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的我回家看电视了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是友绘?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是艾亚利兹共和国总统　雪之·克利桑德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亲自来和你们交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么　乘上巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话我就听你说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换　我要求你们释放人质
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多事情就拜托了呢　准将
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把她也放了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说她是大公殿下最大的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾亚利兹决不会屈服于恐怖主义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.67,0:12:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且　连风花王国都会变成你们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶说过　打女人的男人是最差劲的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧　雪之小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢　爱莉卡也很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我无论如何都想自己去找到真白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是小遥不见的话　我想我也会这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是我不是总统的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之小姐和准将从来不吵架吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我和小遥之间有个规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规矩?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:13:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对　要是我做错的话小遥会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是小遥做错的话　我会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后两个人好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到两人都觉得正确的道路时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就毫不犹豫地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾乃五柱之一　银河的蓝玉　萨拉·加拉格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求备用系统给予认证
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:50.24,Note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(405,420)}Surrogate System
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:53.08,Materialise,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Materialise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小遥一定会做我认为是正确的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的乙HiME　遥·阿米特吉准将
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了　雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐　怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎战　快开火　开火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绑架人质　威胁我们释放那基
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借助别人力量的你们　从一开始就没有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要报仇的话　就用自己的双手　堂堂正正地去做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是子兽?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:48.12,Note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(463,420)}CHILD
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对象认定为敌对性生命体！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DELTA Force　迎战！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遥…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将！雪之小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:16:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥·阿米特吉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持有珠洲之黄玉的吾之乙HiME啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以吾之名　解放汝的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下　准将
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不赖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以总统之名　把你打成碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快去避难　克利桑德阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你　Meister萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人　你看到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不　那位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真祖大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白的金刚石　Grand Meister　二三·姬野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DELTA　Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真祖怎么可能会袭击我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我来揭露你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要抱到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要追得太深
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good Luck！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遥！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要搞背后袭击！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就交给你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将…准将！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:47.91,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,375)}{\fad(600,0)}艾亚利兹境内　Desperate监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾呢　被释放的机会溜掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~那群人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:21:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算跟那些劫持巴士的人走　也很快就会被抓住的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况最后失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无可救药的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说我聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.04,0:21:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一日三餐还能午睡　我挺喜欢这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用像在黑之谷那样被强制劳动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说　黑之谷里发生什么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.72,0:21:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对　黑之谷消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白和舞衣也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.27,0:21:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我　那基先生　大家在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就是说「他」来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不　该说是「她」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到加尔德罗贝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被干掉的乙HiME们的纳米机器发生硬化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有生命反应　身体却硬得像矿石一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的只是很少的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记载在我从阿尔泰的遗迹里找到的文献里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.65,0:22:15.84,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,375)}{\fad(500,450)}{\1c&HC9CAC8&}阿尔泰公国　黑曜宫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:28.20,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,395)}{\fad(500,0)}{\1c&HC9CAC8&}（俗称）　条纹亭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.77,0:22:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在条纹团的根据地办Meister学校真的好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你还说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.98,0:22:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城里的大官们有事的话让他们来这里就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算Peace Maker也和一般的小混混没什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜托你的那个东西呢　小山山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我小山山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.03,0:22:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真打算要去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从回到这里以后我就很闲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这么冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃的东西都那么油腻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:23:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为讨厌这里才去了加尔德罗贝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被降职了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的发泄吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.97,0:23:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛~虽然我不是很赞成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.81,0:23:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听传闻说你们五柱…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.66,0:23:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管闲事　小山山
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister朱丽叶特·奈绪·张
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.82,0:23:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把客人带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了　奈绪前辈
